If you hold Abjcoin in any of these wallets, you would receive Abjcoin Commerce. •   Satowallet.com •   Stocks.Exchange •   Abjcoin Mobile wallet.  Pool Related Issue For a while we have worked tirelessly to resolve all issues from the Abjcoin Pool, for those who have any issue whatsoever on the pool please contact our Support Team, the deadline to contact the team is till Friday 10th of June 2018. To get your mining pool issue resolved send your request to contact@abjcoin.org in this format •   Your emails address (the one you used in creating your Abjcoin mining pool account). •   Your username •   Your new Abjcoin wallet address from any of the listed exchange above. •   The amount of coin to be verified. Kindly note that if your request does not meet the above criteria, your request will not be attended to

Author: Abjcoin Blockchain
Title: ABJCOIN COMMERCE | AIRDROPS | DECENTRALIZED FEE-LESS BLOCKCHAIN MARKETPLACE
Body: Dear Community members and Investors, We want to appreciate you for your support and patient in building the Abjcoin project, we can say without a doubt that Abjcoin has one of the best community and investors in the crypto space. We do understand that the past season has been hard for the Abjcoin team and community due to several occurrences beyond our control which includes Coinmarkets closing up, Coinhouse offline and many more. This has also led to several of our team members and developers, exiting the project. The Abjcoin core team has thought of several ways to solve all these issues arising, and have even thought of making a second chain for the Abjcoin project to run side by side, to enable us have another fresh start. If we had gone ahead with making a new chain, all Abjcoin holders would have gotten part of the new chain on a 10:1 ratio. But after consulting our project advisors, we are made to believe that it will not be the best option. The Abjcoin core team is committed to this project and wants to see it actualize its full potentials. With that in view, the Abjcoin team has decided to restructure the Abjcoin project for better effectiveness and to actualize it potentials. During this restructuring we would be removing several arms of the project to enable us focus on the core. The restructuring will include; 1.   Abjcoin code update to version 2: We will be updating our code and core wallets to a higher blockchain version to solve conflicting issues as regards to mined coins, for better synchronization and transaction speed. We will be releasing a new core wallet version and also upgraded source code on Github. 2.   Abjcoin bug bounty: Before release of version 2 code base, we would be opening up the Abjcoin blockchain for a hacking test. This will enable us to have a better code system that can stand any attack. The bounty winner will be given $10,000 as reward for hack and fix. 3.   macOS Core wallet release: Due to high user demands, we will be releasing the Core wallet for macOS. 4.   Raspberry Core wallet release: Due to high user demands, we will be releasing the Core wallet for Raspberry. 5.   Abjcoin Pool maintenance: For security reasons we would be closing down the Abjcoin pool to solve several issues. Therefore we would require all users to withdraw their coins out of the pool. No new deposit or re-investing will be allowed till further notice. 6.   Telegram group deactivation: As a way to protect the community and new investors from wrong influence, we would be closing the telegram group and converting it to the channel(https://t.me/officialabjcoinchannel).  Users are advised to join the channel for latest info, and also to join us actively on twitter (https://twitter.com/abjcoinblockch). For all the users who are in the group to encourage investors, we do appreciate you, but we would be glad if all those post be done on other open social media to increase our presence. 7.   Project Rebranding: We would be rebranding our project image for better international standards, communication and partnership. 8.   Smart Marketplace App: We would be releasing a new Andriod and IOS App with a smart marketplace running on the Abjcoin blockchain. 9.   Recruitments: We would be recruiting new staffs for in-house work to increase our effectiveness as a team. After completing the above, we would suspend every other roadmap and focus on exchanges and marketing the use cases of Abjcoin. Love the Abjcoin project? Please donate to our project development: F8TmD9Pzx5VLKnBzSgmpZVpG5pfPBVuFJN Thank you for your support and understanding. Abjcoin developers!

Author: Abjcoin Blockchain
Title: ABJCOIN COMMERCE | AIRDROPS | DECENTRALIZED FEE-LESS BLOCKCHAIN MARKETPLACE
Body: Dear AbjCoin Community Members,  We would love to thank you all for your support and commitment along this rough path of growth, AbjCoin is still pulling through because of your die hard belief and unflinching resolve to hold Abjcoin to the very end. This has not only re energized the team members but has also ignited our creative confidence that Abjcoin was developed for greater things.  To this end, we have worn our creative caps to restructure the Abjcoin so as to fulfill all the promises we made to our investors.  Abjcoin will now have a side chain called Abjcoin Commerce (ABJC) , this will not in any way affect the operation of the first Abjcoin, but what we are trying to do is to right our wrongs with the Abjcoin C  The Abjcoin C will come with the following features      It will be listed in bigger exchanges (like you all have suggested)     It will come with its own IOS and Android wallets     Integrated with it’s own decentralized commerce chain in the mobile app, with the ability to sell and buy within the app.  ETC  The Abjcoin Commerce side chain will occur at a certain block on the Abjcoin blockchain that we would announce, and all Abjcoin holders will receive 1 ABJC for every 10 ABJ in their wallets.  The ABJ will also have a smaller supply of 21,000,000 as against the 30,000,000 of Abjcoin.  Secondly this restructuring is inevitable as it is our desire to give all investors value for their money and we strongly believe that will help us in achieving that.  To this end, we will restructure the Abjcoin websites and other social media handles to reflect this change.  We strongly believe that this move will make a difference and help us salvage the current situation. All we ask for is your corporation as usual and we trust this process will be seamless as ever.  We will update you subsequently about all that is expected to happen and how best our community members should position themselves to get the best out of this experience.  Thank You  -The Abjcoin Team

Title: ABJCOIN COMMERCE | AIRDROPS | DECENTRALIZED FEE-LESS BLOCKCHAIN MARKETPLACE
Body: Welcome to the Abjcoin weekly update March 12, 2018 Welcome to the Abjcoin weekly update. In this update we will be focusing on sharing an overview of our work and progress report of some of our projects. we will be giving you further details on the following ; • Abjcoin current price dip • The Abjcoin cryptocurrency Exchange • AirDrop payment Update  1. The Abjcoin current price dip; We are all aware of the current fall (dip) in the Abjcoin price, after a thorough research and analysis was carried out, the team came to a conclusion to the possible fall in price; • Over 500,000 Abjcoin was released to most persons whose coin where withheld to prove their ownership of the coins by conducting a KYC, probably most of these persons decided to dump the coins. • Most persons who got reward from the recent pool and airdrop also decided to sell their coins. • We also suspect that coinsmarkets.com is trying to sell off coins at their disposal. However, we have done all we can to contact them so they allow users to withdraw their Abjcoin but as sad as it sounds, all these have proven futile. However, our resolve is strong, we promise to do anything within our powers to get back those coins. Please don’t forget that the best time to HODL Abjcoin is now.  2. The Abjcoin cryptocurrency exchange; We promised our community to build a world class exchange platform for Abjcoin and other cryptocurrencies, this we have done and we will soon disclose it to the community. Security is one of the biggest features we want this platform to have, to that extent, we are doing all the necessary corrections and security checks to ensure its safety and that the funds of our users are well protected. As soon as the team of experts who are working on it are done, we will make it open for business.  3. The Air Drop payments The Abjcoin balance Airdrop has been concluded and payment made. However, most persons who participated In the airdrop are yet to receive their reward, also must person who participated did not stick to the rules of the airdrop. Incase you are part of those who participated in the airdrop and did not get your reward and you followed the rules, kindly send your wallet address that shows the required amount of coins to contact@abjcoin.org. After proper verification, you will be credited with your reward. We will keep you updated on all our recent projects and development.  Thank you for believing and supporting Abjcoin.

Title: ABJCOIN COMMERCE | AIRDROPS | DECENTRALIZED FEE-LESS BLOCKCHAIN MARKETPLACE
Body: Welcome to the Abjcoin Weekly update for the 5th of March, 2018.    In this update we will be focusing on sharing an overview of our work progress and development update. we will be giving you further details on the following project developments we are working on • Airdrop Payment • More News About listing on Exchanges • Some changes on our operational strategies • Abjcoin Decentralized marketplace (CoineasyBuy.com).  1. Airdrop Payment: We are almost concluding the airdrop payment, those who participated in the airdrop should kindly check the address that was submitted for the Airdrop. Kindly note: This Airdrop is called balance Airdrop; where you are required to hold a particular number of Abjcoins for a specified time, this qualifies and makes you eligible to participate in the airdrop. Read this for more detail: https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2843251.0 to this effect, anybody who violates the law of the airdrop will not get any reward from the airdrop. Thank you for your compliance.  2. More News About Listing on Exchange: We are already in talk with some exchange and we will inform our community after the deal is sealed. We urge our community to be patient with us and trust our approach and process, we ensure you that our team members are ever committed to push Abjcoin to the next level, we understand that the process might not be as fast as we expected it to be, but we have a guiding compass which is our roadmap and we assure you that everything stated on our published roadmap will definitely be completed.  3. Some improvement on our operational strategies: To serve our community better, we are rebranding some of our operational strategies to make it up to date with international best practices. We understand that our community members cut across the globe, we are partnering with more human resource experts and brand to help us meet the needs of our community. More updates will follow subsequently on this.  4. The Abjcoin Decentralized marketplace USD price update (coineasybuy.com); As we are all aware of the Abjcoin decentralized marketplace; Coineasybuy.com is multi-vendor decentralized marketplace for buyers and sellers to pay for good and service with Abjcoin. Coineasybuy USD price has been update to be of equivalent to the price of Abjcoin as seen on Coinmarketcap. With 60,000 goods and services from vendor all around the globe, we encourage our community member to register as vendors by creating a merchants account. Registration and sales is free for both sellers and buyers. More news update will be given shortly about this. Visit www.coinesybuy.com to register today.  We promise to constantly update you on all development. Thank you for supporting Abjcoin.

Author: Abjcoin Blockchain
Title: ABJCOIN COMMERCE | AIRDROPS | DECENTRALIZED FEE-LESS BLOCKCHAIN MARKETPLACE
Body: THE ABJCOIN EXTENDS IT’S REACH TO THE UNITED ARABS     In recent times, the digital market has seen a surge in trades made with cryptocurrency. Following the creation and slow, but steady, rise of Bitcoin since 2009, various altcoins have been created with an estimate of over a thousand cryptocurrency specifications as of September 2017.      Now, ABJCOIN, from the heart of Africa, gives the opportunity to trade freely in the global market. Being the first of its kind cryptocurrency for trade, exchange and payment platform from Africa at large, ABJCOIN is truly Africa's blockchain solution for global payments.  As the major aim of the coin is to provide frictionless ease of transactions between Africa and the rest of the world, little wonder it is that the first African blockchain solution for global payment has made history again. In their bid to spread the good news of blockchain, ABJCOIN has extended its global reach to the United Arab Emirates. On the 6th of January, the whole crypto-community in Dubai came out enmasse at the Dubai mall to hear for themselves the numerous benefits ABJCOIN can do for the economy. Speaking at the occasion, the lead developer of ABJCOIN, Dr. Samuel Benedict said that the sole purpose of the ABJCOIN is to foster trade and commerce from Africa to the rest of the world and that Dubai has one of the most stable economy in the world, thus partnering with ABJCOIN will bring endless business opportunity to the Emirate. Speaking also, Al Mohammed, the group leader for the movement to promote blockchain technology in Dubai said that the blockchain technology is a tool which every economy must learn and take advantage of, and that he believes that ABJCOIN blockchain has a high prospect and would help Dubai achieve its goal of a decentralized system of payment. In addition, the managing director of Blockchain Tech Hub Mr. O. Osiobe also reiterated that the technology and consensus of the ABJCOIN makes it an economy friendly cryptocurrency in terms of transaction fees and speed which has been one of the biggest challenges of some well-known cryptocurrencies in recent times.     Since the proof of stake algorithm of the ABJCOIN makes it easy to mine and it has a transaction speed of 40seconds, this will make service delivery and transfer of value much better. The highlight of the event was the grand opening of the Abjcoin blockchain partnership, the partners are to drive the Abjcoin roadmap in the United Arab Emirate. The event ended with a syndicate session of training on how on to trade and how to create wealth with cryptocurrency. Already over 50 merchants and business in Dubai are ready to accept Abjcoin as a means of payment of goods and services.    https://abjcoin.org/abjcoin-extends-reach-united-arabs/

That ingredient is the ability for Africans to buy this with their local currency. I believe a solution to this would be to create your own in-house exchange that supports the buying and selling of this coin with the Naira at the CBN official rate. Imagine what this will do for businesses that depend on forex. The effect will be so profound. As an example, cryptopia (a New Zealand exchange) supports the purchase of cryptocurrencies with the new zealand dollar. QuadrigaCx (a Canadian exchange) also support purchase of cryptos with the Canadian dollar. You already hold the advantage of being a pioneer in a country of 180million people who desperately need a reliable and fair forex platform. Nigeria is your market so look no further. When you capture Nigeria, the whole world would notice ABJCOIN and come knocking on your door. Keep the good work.

Body: This coin has the potential to succeed in Africa. Africa has already shown the world the way how Mobile payments could be streamlined in the business world. This is another opportunity where ABJ coin can indeed succeed in facilitating online-commerce in Africa and undoubtedly in other parts of the world. Bitcoin can be argued to provide the same functionality but with its seething problems: higher transaction costs, longer transaction confirmation times and higher withdrawal minimums make it an unattractive solution not just for Africa but for the rest of the world. Good luck!

Because Bitcoin is so big, it takes too much time for people to agree on innovative changes. This is why there was a huge surge in alternative currencies last few years.  AbjCoin focuses on privacy and transaction. Therefore makes use of the Scrypt POW/POS algorithms, as against the POW of bitcoin that gives big miners the ability to decide the outcome of bitcoin without the masses participating.  AbjCoin proof of stake algorithms makes everyone a miner , through a system called staking.  Proof of Stake verse Proof of Work                                                                                                                                                Proof-of-Work was a fantastic innovation that formed the backbone of the original Bitcoin protocol. The idea is that by solving a computationally intensive math problem, one can prove the effort they’ve done to secure the protocol. This is how a blockchain is generated, and the effort that is required to perform this computations contribute to a coin’s scarcity and value.However, Proof-of-Work eventually becomes an extraordinarily expensive system.Proof of Stake solves this issue in a very elegant way. Rather than using computer power as a scarce resource to generate security, Proof of Stake uses the scarcity of the coin itself. A user may choose to “stake” his coins to generate the next block in the chain, and his chance of doing so is basically proportional to the weight of his own coins.  Proof-of-Stake is eco-friendly and efficient, and avoids the vast waste of energy and hardware overhead of Proof-of-Work based networks. AbjCoin however combine both
